---
layout: base.njk
title: An Interactive Brand Marketing Agency in Canada | Promo Your Biz
description: An Interactive Brand Marketing Agency in Canada
showLearnMoreButton: true
---

<main>
  <header class="header-dm section-padding">
    <div class="container position-re">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-9">
          <div class="caption">
            <h1> Unleash the Power of <br /> Your Brand&apos;s Story</h1>
            <a href="https://calendly.com/ca-promoyourbiz/book-your-free-15-min-website-audit-promoyourbiz-ca" class="crv-butn mt-40" style="background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <span class="text">Get Free Website Audit Session</span>
                <span class="icon">
                  <img src="/common/imgs/icons/arrow-top-right.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="row md-hide">
            <div class="col-lg-6 imgs-cube">
              <div class="imgs">
                <div class="circle">
                  <img src="/assets/imgs/header/circle-badge.svg" alt="" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="img fit-img radius-30 mt-50">
                <video src="/assets/imgs/header/video-1.mp4" autoplay muted loop></video>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mimg fit-img">
        <div class="shaps top">
          <div class="shap-right-top">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-11 h-11">
              <path d="M11 1.54972e-06L0 0L2.38419e-07 11C1.65973e-07 4.92487 4.92487 1.62217e-06 11 1.54972e-06Z" fill="#232323"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="shap-left-bottom">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-11 h-11">
              <path d="M11 1.54972e-06L0 0L2.38419e-07 11C1.65973e-07 4.92487 4.92487 1.62217e-06 11 1.54972e-06Z" fill="#232323"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <video style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; border-radius: 30px" src="/assets/imgs/header/video-222.mp4" autoplay muted loop></video>
        <div class="text">
          <span class="fz-12 text-u mb-10">Since 2018</span>
          <p>We craft websites that reveal your why <br /> and resonate with your audience, <br />turning casual visitors into devoted customers.</p>
          <div class="shaps bottom">
            <div class="shap-left-top">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-11 h-11">
                <path d="M11 1.54972e-06L0 0L2.38419e-07 11C1.65973e-07 4.92487 4.92487 1.62217e-06 11 1.54972e-06Z" fill="#232323"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="shap-right-bottom">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-11 h-11">
                <path d="M11 1.54972e-06L0 0L2.38419e-07 11C1.65973e-07 4.92487 4.92487 1.62217e-06 11 1.54972e-06Z" fill="#232323"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro-dm">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-head mb-25">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h2 class="mb-40">Why Your Brand Matters</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h6 class="font-normal">Every brand has a spark that sets it apart. We believe your origin story, values, and vision are the most powerful assets you own. By centering your website around your why, you will connect with customers on a deeper level—fostering loyalty and advocacy rather than fleeting clicks.
            </h6>
            <a href="/about/" class="crv-butn mt-40">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <span class="text">More About Us</span>
                <span class="icon">
                  <img src="/common/imgs/icons/arrow-top-right.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="works-dm pt-30 pb-30">
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-40">Our Featured Work</h2>
        <h6>Take a look at our projects. We've had the privilege of collaborating with businesses across diverse industries, helping them establish a strong online presence and achieve their digital goals.</h6>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery row md-marg">
        {% for item in portfolio | shuffle | slice(0, 4) %}
        <div class="items col-lg-6 order-md-2">
          <div class="item">
            <div class="img">
              <img src="{{ item.image }}" alt="" />
              <div class="tags">
                {% for tag in item.tags %}
                <a href="#0">{{ tag }}</a>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cont mt-30">
              <div class="info sub-color mb-10">
                <span>{{ item.created }}</span>
                <span class="dot"></span>
                <span>{% for tech in item.technologies %}{{ tech }}{% endfor %}</span>
              </div>
              <h6>
                <a class="font-bold" target="_blank" href="{{ item.link }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
              </h6>
              <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <a href="/portfolio/" class="crv-butn mt-100">
            <div class="d-flex">
              <span class="text">View all Projects</span>
              <span class="icon">
                <img src="/common/imgs/icons/arrow-top-right.svg" alt="" />
              </span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include 'services.njk' %}

  <section class="intro-vid ontop">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bg-img" data-background="/assets/imgs/pyb-intro-video-snap.png">
        <div class="states">
          <h3 class="mb-15">100+ Projects</h3>
          <p>We have successfully delivered over 100 projects for our clients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="play-button">
          <a href="/assets/videos/pyb-intro-video.mp4" class="vid">
            <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="mt-100">
    {% include 'testimonials.njk' %}
  </div>

  <section class="blog-sa">
    <div class="container section-padding">
      <div class="sec-head mb-30">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h2 class="mb-40">Latest Articles</h2>
            <h6>The place that we share everything related to design trends, tips and more.
            </h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        {% for post in collections.blog | reverse | slice(0, 2) %}
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="item{% if loop.first %} md-mb50{% endif %}">
            <div>
              <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="cont mt-30">
              <h6>
                <a class="font-bold" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
              </h6>
              <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
              <div class="info d-flex align-items-center mt-20">
                <a href="#0" class="tag">
                  <span>{{ post.data.tag }}</span>
                </a>
                <a href="#0" class="date">
                  <span>/ {{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <a href="/blogs/" class="crv-butn mt-100">
            <div class="d-flex">
              <span class="text">View all Blogs</span>
              <span class="icon">
                <img src="/common/imgs/icons/arrow-top-right.svg" alt="" />
              </span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
